SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AddedBy], [p].[DateAdded], [p].[DateModified], [p].[Description], [p].[IsScheme], [p].[ModifiedBy], [p].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[AddedById], [p0].[ClientId], [p0].[ClientStatusId], [p0].[DateAdded], [p0].[DateModified], [p0].[IsWithdrawal], [p0].[ModifiedById], [p0].[PortfolioId]

    FROM [AspnetUserPortfolio] AS [a]

ORDER BY [p].[Name], [p].[Id]

     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0

         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )
)
SELECT 1 ELSE SELECT 0
